First if you are using VMachine
configure network setting in your virtual machine go to settings network advanced, change from NAT to bridge Adapter and you choose a wireless one or ethernet one.
change time zone to be same as the real time clock, on the top right of your kali linux there is clock ,right click it and choose properties ,write down your timezone and you good to go
now open your terminal and type the following commands that will configure your kali linux
sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list
the results you will get add an "s" to all http you are seeing,at the #deb-src http://http.kali.org/kali remove the # symbol and press CTRL+X and Y then ENTER
write down the following commands in your terminal
sudo apt install apt-transport-https   //and press ENTER
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade    //and press ENTER.. this will take a long time be patient
sudo apt install git  //this will install git
sudo apt install tor  //this will install tor
sudo apt install torbrowser-launcher //and press ENTER
sudo apt install tilix  //this will install terminal multiplexer will allow you to split terminal as many as you want
sudo apt install metasploit-framework  //this will install metasploit
sudo apt install set  //will install social engineering
sudo apt install cmatrix  //this will install CMATRIX

sudo apt update
sudo apt install sqlmap  //this will install sqlmap
